OL,5, Britain's first openly gay senior judge
OL,6, will lead a review into the impact of  
OL,7, an historic ban on LGBT people serving 
OL,8, in the armed forces.                   
OL,10,FLord Etherton's inquiry will look at   
OL,11,Fhow those affected can be redressed.   
OL,13,FCampaigners are hoping for compensation
OL,14,Ffor lost livelihoods and suffering as  
OL,15,Fwell as mental health support.         
OL,17,FThe review will apply to veterans who  
OL,18,Fserved between 1967, when homosexual   
OL,19,Facts began to be decriminalised, and   
OL,20,F2000.                                  
